{"title":"使用lombok注解简化代码开发","date":"2019-11-04T03:28:47.000Z","link":"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发","tags":["Java"],"updated":"2019-11-04T03:49:04.000Z","content":"<h4 id=\"lombok可以使用注解来简化java的开发，虽然idea有快捷键Alt-insert组合键可以添加构造函数，get-set-toString等方法，但是这样代码量会显得冗长且缺乏技术含量，使用lombok就可以解决这个问题\">lombok可以使用注解来简化java的开发，虽然idea有快捷键Alt+insert组合键可以添加构造函数，get/set/toString等方法，但是这样代码量会显得冗长且缺乏技术含量，使用lombok就可以解决这个问题<a href=\"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发#lombok可以使用注解来简化java的开发，虽然idea有快捷键Alt-insert组合键可以添加构造函数，get-set-toString等方法，但是这样代码量会显得冗长且缺乏技术含量，使用lombok就可以解决这个问题\"></a></h4><p>首先添加pom.xml依赖</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.projectlombok<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>lombok<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">version</span>&gt;</span>1.16.20<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">scope</span>&gt;</span>provided<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">scope</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>然后就可以使用了</p>\n<h4 id=\"Data\">@Data<a href=\"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发#Data\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@Data</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">User</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title\">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> Integer id;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> String username;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> String password;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>这个@Data拥有开头所说的get/set等方法，或者</p>\n<h4 id=\"Getter-Setter\">@Getter @Setter<a href=\"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发#Getter-Setter\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">User</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title\">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Getter</span> <span class=\"meta\">@Setter</span> <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> Integer id;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Getter</span> <span class=\"meta\">@Setter</span> <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> String username;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Getter</span> <span class=\"meta\">@Setter</span> <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> String password;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Cleanup\">@Cleanup<a href=\"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发#Cleanup\"></a></h4><p>此注解将会自动电泳close()方法，简化代码且避免忘记关闭一些io</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@Cleanup</span> InputStream in = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileInputStream(file);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>一般用到的就这几个，还有一些不太常用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"使用idea插件解决对象无法使用-Data注解的类方法问题\">使用idea插件解决对象无法使用@Data注解的类方法问题<a href=\"2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发#使用idea插件解决对象无法使用-Data注解的类方法问题\"></a></h3><p>虽然@Data方便，但是在开发中，如果要调用.setName()方法时，会发现无法调用，这是因为在源码级别没有set方法，lombok使用注解是编译成class文件时会把get/set方法加入的，因此需要安装idea插件。<br><img src=\"http://148.70.50.70/source/1572833796181.jpg\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>完毕</p>\n","prev":{"title":"SpringBoot异常处理","link":"2019/11/06/SpringBoot异常处理"},"next":{"title":"StudyPlan","link":"2019/10/31/StudyPlan"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/11/04/使用lombok注解简化代码开发/"}